entor-element-dc026dd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dc026dd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.17.0 - 08-11-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p>L\u2019ANLC-PBG \u00e0 travers son service d\u2019alerte re\u00e7oit et g\u00e8re les signalements d\u2019actes de corruption. A cet effet elle s\u2019occupe de :<\/p><ul><li>La Gestion des plaintes : L\u2019ANLC s\u2019occupe de la r\u00e9ception, l\u2019analyse et du traitement des diff\u00e9rentes plaintes re\u00e7ues. Elle d\u00e9cide d\u2019engager ou non des enqu\u00eates et poursuites \u00e0 l\u2019encontre des pr\u00e9sum\u00e9s accus\u00e9s.<\/li><li>La Protection des d\u00e9nonciateurs : L\u2019ANLC s\u2019engage \u00e0 prot\u00e9ger tous les d\u00e9nonciateurs mais aussi les plaignants dans les affaires de corruption. Elle s\u2019engage \u00e0 sauvegarder leur int\u00e9grit\u00e9 physique et morale et \u00e0 les accompagner dans leur d\u00e9marche de r\u00e9clamation ou de d\u00e9nonciation.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-f135fdf elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f135fdf\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8ae41b7\" data-id=\"8ae41b7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2fb826d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2fb826d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pr\u00e9vention<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-87d4a58 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"87d4a58\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"525\" height=\"452\" src=\"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/sensibilisation.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3322\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/sensibilisation.jpg 735w, https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/sensibilisation-300x258.jpg 300w, https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/sensibilisation-370x320.jpg 370w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-66 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-bc4f6b8\" data-id=\"bc4f6b8\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3c9e1d6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3c9e1d6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>L\u2019ANLC-PBG met un certain accent sur la pr\u00e9vention contre la corruption cela par l\u2019\u00e9ducation, la sensibilisation, la formation.<\/p><p>Dans ce cadre elle :<\/p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00c9value les risques de corruption dans les organisations<\/li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00c9duque les communaut\u00e9s sur la corruption<\/li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Organise des conf\u00e9rences et s\u00e9minaires sur la corruption<\/li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Facilite la formation de clubs de jeunes anti-corruption<\/li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Forme des militants anti-corruption (agents publics\/membres de la communaut\u00e9)<\/li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Forme les comit\u00e9s d\u2019int\u00e9grit\u00e9<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-943877a elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"943877a\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-19bb26d\" data-id=\"19bb26d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e42cf14 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e42cf14\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">R\u00e9pression<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f2c7430 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f2c7430\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"525\" height=\"452\" src=\"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/repression.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3321\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/repression.jpg 735w, https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/repression-300x258.jpg 300w, https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/repression-370x320.jpg 370w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-66 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b4fb3b4\" data-id=\"b4fb3b4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c0daba1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c0daba1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Le d\u00e9partement d\u2019investigation de l\u2019ANLC m\u00e8ne des enqu\u00eates sur les d\u00e9lits de corruption \u00e9nonc\u00e9s dans le code p\u00e9nal.<\/p><p>Si la commission est avertie de l&#8217;existence de l&#8217;un de ces d\u00e9lits, il m\u00e8ne imm\u00e9diatement une enqu\u00eate qui consiste \u00e0 rassembler les documents et les preuves pertinents, \u00e0 convoquer les suspects et les t\u00e9moins potentiels pour les interroger et \u00e0 effectuer des recherches suppl\u00e9mentaires sur l&#8217;affaire. Une fois l&#8217;enqu\u00eate termin\u00e9e, un rapport d&#8217;enqu\u00eate est r\u00e9dig\u00e9 sur la base des conclusions et des preuves recueillies.<\/p><p>Le rapport d&#8217;enqu\u00eate est pr\u00e9sent\u00e9 aux membres de la Commission, qui prennent alors une d\u00e9cision sur l&#8217;affaire. Si l&#8217;affaire implique une corruption, elle est transmise au bureau du procureur.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>D\u00e9tection L\u2019ANLC-PBG \u00e0 travers son service d\u2019alerte re\u00e7oit et g\u00e8re les signalements d\u2019actes de corruption. A cet effet elle s\u2019occupe de : La Gestion des plaintes : L\u2019ANLC s\u2019occupe de [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"tpl-default-elementor.php","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2087"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2087"}],"version-history":[{"count":196,"href":"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2087\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3796,"href":"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2087\/revisions\/3796"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/anlcpbg.gov.gn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2087"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}